text: Kjell Voll (born 12 March 1966) is a Norwegian rower. He competed in the men's double sculls event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Norwegian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Norway Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stavanger
